<emphasis id="67DFEAE5FFBCFFCED425FAB0FE391032" box="[353,486,1286,1310]" italics="true" pageId="19" pageNumber="158">(Baker) Parris</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<emphasis id="67DFEAE5FFBCFFCED4A9FAB0FDB0107F" italics="true" pageId="19" pageNumber="158">but differs from this species by the lamina shorter and narrower, 4-11 × 0.2-0.9 cm (vs 10-36 × 1.8- 5.5 cm) and proximal segments gradually decreasing.</emphasis>
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
